Objective
Find a Peach

Be careful there are various guards around each area. With varying difficulty

Strength Stealth
Dexterity Stealth
Wisdom Stealth

Look through a window of an obelisk/tower to see everything around you.
Can be used by anyone.
Can only be used one at a time even if there is multiple towers.
It takes 10 minutes to use



Layout

A Hexagonal shape starting point with 6 different directions leading to different areas.

To complete the floor they must find the golden peach.

Will need to succeed various checks in each areas while also avoiding patrol guards.

Only 1 may do the check. A failure will require the player to fight off the guards and run back to the center.

Each check will be assigned a random set of minutes that is needed to perform. A Nat 1 will double the time of attempt while a NAT 20 will halve the time needed.

Make either an ability check 1d6
1) Strength
2) Dexterity
3) Constitution
4) Intelligence
5) Wisdom
6) Charisma

Or 3 random skill check  3d18
1) Athletics
2) Acrobatics
3) Sleight of Hand
4) Stealth
5) Arcana
6) History
7) Investigation
8) Nature
9) Religion
10) Animal Handling
11) Insight
